1 1/4 cups oat flour
1 cup flour
1/4 tsp salt (omit if butter is salted)
1/2 tsp baking powder
1/2 tsp baking soda
1/2 cup butter (unsalted)
1/2 cup white sugar
1/2 cup brown sugar
1 egg
1 tsp vanilla
1 cup chocolate chips

Choice:
- 1/3 cups nuts, optional (walnuts or pecans)
- 1tbsp flour

Optional:
1 1/2 tsp instant coffee

Bake 375 nonconvention 10-12min, cool 5min
Or bake 300F nonconvection 20min, cool 5min (crispier)
